name: Prestige Star Guardian Neeko (2022)
description: Neeko and the Star Guardians emerge from their battle forever changed, friendships reforged in the face of stunning victory and brutal loss. They will save their lost companion—perhaps not now, but one day—and they will do it together.

wikiSkinData.distribution: Given to players who owned the original skin prior to patch 12.5
